              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-sm rounded-full">OpenAI</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 text-sm rounded-full">Vector DB</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <strong>Kết quả:</strong>học tập 
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <a href="https://github.com/tandat8896/rag_qa_pdf_project1" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-md transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
                </svg>
                View Project
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- MLOps Pipeline Project -->
          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">MLOps Pipeline</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">DevOps & Automation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Xây dựng pipeline MLOps hoàn chỉnh với CI/CD, model versioning, 
              monitoring và auto-retraining cho các mô hình ML trong production.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm rounded-full">Docker</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-sm rounded-full">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-sm rounded-full">MLflow</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 text-sm rounded-full">GitHub Actions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <strong>Kết quả:</strong> Giảm 80% thời gian deploy, tăng 95% model reliability
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <a href="https://github.com/tandat8896/dvc-feast" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-md transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
                </svg>
                View Project
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          

          <!-- Time Series Forecasting -->
          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Time Series Forecasting</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Predictive Analytics</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Sales Forcasting and Demand Predict by Using LightGBM and XAI .
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm rounded-full">Python</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-sm rounded-full">Prophet</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-sm rounded-full">LSTM</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 text-sm rounded-full">ARIMA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <strong>Kết quả:</strong> 85% accuracy trong dự báo, giảm 30% inventory cost
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <a href="https://github.com/tandat8896/sale-forcasting" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-md transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
                </svg>
                View Project
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

      <!-- Skills Section -->
      <section class="py-16">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Kỹ Năng Chuyên Môn</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Các công nghệ và kỹ năng đã học và áp dụng trong các dự án
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Machine Learning</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Scikit-learn, XGBoost, LightGBM, SHAP, LIME</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Deep Learning</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">PyTorch, TensorFlow, OpenCV, YOLO, CNN</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">MLOps</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Docker, Kubernetes, MLflow, GitHub Actions</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">NLP & LLM</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">LangChain, OpenAI, RAG, Transformers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Copyright at bottom -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        <span>Copyright © 2025 | All rights reserved.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BlockLayout>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", () => {
    const indexLayout = (document.querySelector("#main-content") as HTMLElement)
      ?.dataset?.layout;
    if (indexLayout) {
      sessionStorage.setItem("backUrl", "/");
    }
  });
</script>
